<TEI xmlns="http://www.tei-c.org/ns/1.0" xmlns:frus="http://history.state.gov/frus/ns/1.0"><text><body><div frus:doc-dateTime-max="1945-08-11T23:59:59-05:00" frus:doc-dateTime-min="1945-08-11T00:00:00-05:00" n="415" subtype="historical-document" type="document" xml:id="d415">
                                <note rend="inline" type="source">740.00119 P.W./8–1145:
                                    Telegram</note>
                                <head>
                                    <hi rend="italic">The Ambassador in the United Kingdom</hi>
                                        (<persName type="from"><hi rend="italic">Winant</hi></persName>) <hi rend="italic">to the <gloss type="to">Secretary of State</gloss>
                                    </hi>
                                </head>
                                <opener>
                                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                                        <placeName>
                                            <hi rend="smallcaps">London</hi></placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1945-08-11">August 11,
                                            1945</date>.<lb/>[Received August 11—3:15
                                        p.m.]</dateline>
                                </opener>
                                <p>2263. I have been asked to forward to you the following message:
                                        <quote rend="blockquote">
                                        <p>“His Majesty’s Government have received your
                                            communication to the Swiss Government for the <hi rend="smallcaps">Japanese</hi> Government, and
                                            agree.”</p>
                                    </quote>
                                </p>
                                <p>The acceptance of the British suggestions in the final text was
                                    deeply appreciated here.</p>
                                <closer>
                                    <signed>
                                        <hi rend="smallcaps">Winant</hi>
                                    </signed>
                                </closer>
                            </div>
                            </body></text></TEI>